com.tinkerpop.frames

Class FramedGraphConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.frames.FramedGraphConfiguration

  • public class FramedGraphConfiguration
extends Object
    A configuration for a FramedGraph. These are supplied to Modules for each FramedGraph being create by a FramedGraphFactory. Allows registration of AnnotationHandlers, FrameInitializers and TypeResolvers.
    Author:
    Bryn Cooke
